ZH: 我们不能轻易舍弃努力的结果。
EN: We should not easily abandon the fruits of our hard work.

ZH: 他舍弃了高薪工作，选择了追求自己的梦想。
EN: He gave up a high-paying job and chose to pursue his dreams.

ZH: 她舍弃了自己的休息时间，全力帮助朋友。
EN: She sacrificed her own rest time and fully helped her friend.

ZH: 这个项目他决定舍弃了，因为没有收益。
EN: He decided to abandon this project because there was no profit.

ZH: 她终于舍弃了对他的不切实际的幻想。
EN: She finally let go of her unrealistic fantasies about him.

ZH: 我舍弃了购物的习惯，节约了很多钱。
EN: I gave up the habit of shopping and saved a lot of money.

ZH: 这位球员舍弃了个人荣誉，选择了和队友合作。
EN: This player sacrificed personal glory and chose to cooperate with his teammates.

ZH: 在面对困难时，我们不能轻易舍弃。
EN: We should not easily give up when facing difficulties.

ZH: 她决定舍弃了上大学的机会，选择了创业。
EN: She decided to abandon the opportunity to go to college and chose to start her own business.

ZH: 不要轻易舍弃一个人的友谊，这是一种宝贵的财富。
EN: Do not easily give up on a person's friendship; it is a precious treasure.

ZH: 这个国家不能舍弃环境的保护。
EN: This country cannot neglect environmental protection.

ZH: 我们要舍弃一些不必要的东西，才能真正富有。
EN: We need to let go of unnecessary things in order to truly be wealthy.

ZH: 这个项目的成本太高，我们只好舍弃了。
EN: The cost of this project is too high, so we have to give it up.

ZH: 为了家庭的幸福，他舍弃了自己的事业。
EN: For the sake of family happiness, he gave up his own career.

ZH: 不要轻易舍弃自己的梦想，努力去追求它们。
EN: Do not easily abandon your dreams; strive to pursue them.

ZH: 我舍弃了手机的使用，专心学习了一个月。
EN: I gave up using my phone and focused on studying for a month.

ZH: 他舍弃了自己的自由，全心为国家服务。
EN: He sacrificed his own freedom and devoted himself to serving the country.

ZH: 这个球队舍弃了对手的一次进攻机会。
EN: The team denied the opponent's scoring opportunity.

ZH: 在求学过程中，我们必须舍弃一些不良习惯。
EN: In the process of studying, we must abandon some bad habits.

ZH: 母亲舍弃了自己的休息时间，照顾生病的孩子。
EN: The mother sacrificed her own rest time to take care of her sick child.

ZH: 这个公司决定舍弃过时的产品线，转向新的市场。
EN: The company decided to abandon the outdated product line and turn to new markets.
